A [[Main/en/Advanced Settings|setting]] that allows you to change how long error messages are displayed for before automatically closing.

== Description ==
This patch allows you to change the duration for which error messages (in the red dialogs) are displayed before automatically closing.

== Use ==
This feature is set to 5 seconds by default. Modify the duration through the [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Interface#Duration of error message|configure patches -> construction]] window or use the following syntax in [[Main/en/openttd.cfg]]:
<pre>[patches]
errmsg_duration = (number of seconds)</pre>

